title: The Commitments-Original Soundtrack, Vol 1 and 2. EAC FLAC
description:
To mark the very recent release of this movie on Blu-Ray, here are FLAC versions of the two CD's that form the musical backdrop of probably the best movie ever made, with the best soundtrack in existance. 

If you haven't seen the movie, then you have missed one of the true masterworks. The performances are truly credible and the development of the intra-character relationships are subtle and complex enough for a doctoral thesis. 

The audio quality is also exceptional. Warm, liquid and supremely dynamic
